As a leader, manager or entrepreneur, your prosperity depends on your comm=
itment to creativity andinnovation=2E Competitive advantage in all areas i=
s shifting to yourability to generate new useful product ideas=2E If you d=
o not innovate,you could fall behind your competitors=2E However, the key =
challenge is,only one in 3000-5000 ideas goes on to be a product (either g=
oodsor services) while others wither away=2E Can this uncertain science be=
 demystified=3F =09=09=09 =20

=09=09=09  This semi-monthly newsletter by Kore Kalibre, titled =09=09=09 =
 Creativityand  Innovation,is designed to provoke thought on novel product=
s=2E How can you generate ideas that have higher probability of success=3F=
 If you have an existing line of products, how can you add complementary p=
roducts=3F  This newsletter has answers to key questions, practical ideas =
and much more=2E
